Interface BuildLog

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractBuildLog
public interface BuildLog
Callback interface used to provide Builder output logging.
Since:
2.3.0
Author:
Phillip Webb, Scott Frederick, Andrey Shlykov, Rafael Ceccone
